      <div class="block__section">
        <p>Donating to the Big Change Fund is an effective way to support people who are homeless. By providing the practical items they need to build new lives off the streets, such as rent deposits and training courses, you are helping individuals to make lasting changes.</p>
        <p>This central fund brings together charities, organisations and people who want to end homelessness to use donations effectively to support change. If everyone who lives, works or visits Manchester donates, together we can make Big Changes in our city!</p>
        <p class="text-center">
          <a href="http://campaign.justgiving.com/charity/forevermanchester/bigchangemcr" class="btn btn--brand-e btn--full">
            <span class="btn__text">Donate to Big Change</span>
          </a>
        </p>
        <a href="http://campaign.justgiving.com/charity/forevermanchester/bigchangemcr" class="display-block">
          <figure class="logo">
            <img src="../../../assets/img/justgiving.png" alt="Just Giving" />
