          <div class="card__footer">
            <p>If the request is for over £100, the application must be agreed by the Big Change panel.</p>
            <p>The Big Change panel includes: one ex-rough sleeper who is in long term support; one representative from an established organisation; two from Coalition of Relief;  and one from CityCo.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

