        <h2 class="h2">How can I find out more about the Big Change Fund?</h2>
        <p>To see a list of the charities and organisations partnered with the Big Change Fund, to find out more about how your donation is used, and to enquire about your organisation becoming an approved partner, please visit the <a href="about">About Big Change Manchester page</a>.</p>
        <p>If you have a specific question, you can contact the Big Change Secretary on 0345 1122211 or email <a href="mailto:bigchange@streetsupport.net">bigchange@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>
        <p>Read the latest <a href="http://news.streetsupport.net/tag/big-change-mcr/">Big Change News</a>, or follow us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/streetsupport">Facebook</a> or <a href="https://twitter.com/streetsupportuk">Twitter</a> to keep up to date with the latest information about Big Change and homelessness in Manchester.</p>
